      "html": "<style data-kid=\"0\">\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');\n  @import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont/tabler-icons.min.css');\n\n  .font-display { font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif; }\n  .font-body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }\n\n  .bento-card {\n    background: #0e0e0e;\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\n    border-radius: 24px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  }\n  .bento-card:hover {\n    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\n  }\n\n  .pill-btn {\n    border-radius: 40px;\n    padding: 12px 24px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    transition: transform 0.2s ease;\n  }\n  .pill-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }\n\n  .marquee-content {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 24px;\n    animation: marquee 40s linear infinite;\n  }\n\n  @keyframes marquee {\n    0% { transform: translateX(0); }\n    100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }\n  }\n\n  .glass-glow {\n    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"bg-[#000000] text-white font-body min-h-screen\" data-kid=\"1\">\n  \n  <nav class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-8 py-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto\" data-kid=\"2\">\n    <div class=\"text-xl font-bold font-display tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"3\">EDUCA PERÚ</div>\n    <div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-sm font-medium text-white/60\" data-kid=\"4\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"5\">Capacitaciones</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"6\">Nosotros</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"7\">Desarrollo Web</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"bg-white text-black px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-bold\" data-kid=\"8\">Ingresar</a>\n    </div>\n  </nav>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"relative pt-24 pb-32 px-6 overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"9\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 glass-glow pointer-events-none\" data-kid=\"10\"></div>\n    <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10\" data-kid=\"11\">\n      <div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 mb-8\" data-kid=\"12\">\n        <i class=\"ti ti-sparkles text-xs\" data-kid=\"13\"></i>\n        <span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"14\">Diseño Web Premium</span>\n      </div>\n      \n      <h1 class=\"font-display text-6xl md:text-8xl font-medium tracking-[-0.05em] leading-[0.9] mb-8\" data-kid=\"15\">\n        Tu negocio, ahora en el<br data-kid=\"16\">nivel que merece.\n      </h1>\n      \n      <p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-white/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"17\">\n        Diseñamos páginas web que transmiten confianza, atraen clientes y hacen crecer tus ventas. Sin complicaciones técnicas para ti.\n      </p>\n      \n      <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"18\">\n        <a href=\"#contacto\" class=\"pill-btn bg-white text-black text-sm flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"19\">\n          Hablar con un experto\n          <i class=\"ti ti-arrow-right\" data-kid=\"20\"></i>\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"#proceso\" class=\"pill-btn bg-white/10 text-white text-sm\" data-kid=\"21\">Ver nuestro proceso</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"py-24 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto\" data-kid=\"22\">\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\" data-kid=\"23\">\n      \n      <div class=\"md:col-span-2 bento-card relative min-h-[400px] group\" data-kid=\"24\">\n        <div class=\"p-8 relative z-10\" data-kid=\"25\">\n          <h3 class=\"text-3xl font-display font-medium mb-2 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"26\">Vende las 24 horas</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-white/60 max-w-sm\" data-kid=\"27\">Tiendas online optimizadas para que tus clientes compren en cualquier momento, desde cualquier lugar.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-3/4 h-3/4 overflow-hidden rounded-tl-3xl border-t border-l border-white/10 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105\" data-kid=\"28\">\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1757301714935-c8127a21abc6?auto=format&w=800&q=80&fit=crop\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" alt=\"Checkout Mockup\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-kid=\"29\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"bento-card p-8 flex flex-col justify-between\" data-kid=\"30\">\n        <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border border-white/10 mb-6\" data-kid=\"31\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-device-mobile text-2xl\" data-kid=\"32\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"33\">\n          <h3 class=\"text-xl font-display font-medium mb-2 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"34\">Increíble en celulares</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-sm text-white/60\" data-kid=\"35\">El 80% de tus clientes te buscará desde su móvil. Estarás listo para ellos.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"bento-card p-8 flex flex-col justify-between\" data-kid=\"36\">\n        <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border border-white/10 mb-6\" data-kid=\"37\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-sliders text-2xl\" data-kid=\"38\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"39\">\n          <h3 class=\"text-xl font-display font-medium mb-2 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"40\">Tú tienes el control</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-sm text-white/60\" data-kid=\"41\">Sistemas intuitivos para que actualices tus fotos y textos sin depender de nadie.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"md:col-span-2 bento-card p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"42\">\n        <div class=\"flex-1\" data-kid=\"43\">\n          <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border border-white/10 mb-6\" data-kid=\"44\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-shield-check text-2xl\" data-kid=\"45\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-display font-medium mb-2 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"46\">Seguridad total</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-white/60\" data-kid=\"47\">Tu sitio web estará protegido contra ataques y siempre en línea. Blindamos tu presencia digital.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex-1 w-full h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center\" data-kid=\"48\">\n            \n            <div class=\"flex gap-2\" data-kid=\"49\">\n                <div class=\"w-1 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"50\"></div>\n                <div class=\"w-1 h-16 bg-white/40 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"51\"></div>\n                <div class=\"w-1 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"52\"></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section id=\"proceso\" class=\"py-32 px-6 border-y border-white/5 bg-[#050505]\" data-kid=\"53\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 md:gap-32\" data-kid=\"54\">\n      <div class=\"md:w-1/3 md:sticky md:top-32 h-fit\" data-kid=\"55\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-medium tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight\" data-kid=\"56\">Tu nueva web<br data-kid=\"57\">en 3 pasos.</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-white/40\" data-kid=\"58\">Simplificamos el proceso técnico para que tú te enfoques en lo que mejor sabes hacer: manejar tu negocio.</p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"md:w-2/3 space-y-24\" data-kid=\"59\">\n        <div class=\"flex gap-8 group\" data-kid=\"60\">\n          <div class=\"text-7xl font-display font-bold text-transparent\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\" data-kid=\"61\">1</div>\n          <div class=\"pt-4\" data-kid=\"62\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-display font-medium mb-3\" data-kid=\"63\">Charlamos</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"64\">Entendemos tu negocio, quiénes son tus clientes y qué necesitas lograr. No hablamos en código, hablamos de objetivos.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"flex gap-8 group\" data-kid=\"65\">\n          <div class=\"text-7xl font-display font-bold text-transparent\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\" data-kid=\"66\">2</div>\n          <div class=\"pt-4\" data-kid=\"67\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-display font-medium mb-3\" data-kid=\"68\">Diseñamos</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"69\">Te presentamos una propuesta visual espectacular. Verás cómo lucirá tu sitio antes de que empecemos a construirlo.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"flex gap-8 group\" data-kid=\"70\">\n          <div class=\"text-7xl font-display font-bold text-transparent\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\" data-kid=\"71\">3</div>\n          <div class=\"pt-4\" data-kid=\"72\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-display font-medium mb-3\" data-kid=\"73\">Lanzamos</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"74\">Ponemos tu web en línea y te entregamos las llaves. Te enseñamos a usarla para que tengas el control total.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"py-32 overflow-hidden bg-black\" data-kid=\"75\">\n    <div class=\"px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto mb-16 text-center\" data-kid=\"76\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-4xl font-display font-medium tracking-tight mb-4\" data-kid=\"77\">Elegancia en cada pixel</h2>\n      <p class=\"text-white/40\" data-kid=\"78\">Resultados reales para empresas que buscan destacar.</p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"flex marquee-container\" data-kid=\"79\">\n      <div class=\"marquee-content\" data-kid=\"80\">\n        \n        <div class=\"w-[500px] h-[300px] bg-[#0e0e0e] rounded-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden shrink-0\" data-kid=\"81\">\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1634744536075-d22f42f88e54?auto=format&w=800&q=80&fit=crop\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80\" alt=\"Mockup 1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-kid=\"82\">\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"w-[500px] h-[300px] bg-[#0e0e0e] rounded-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden shrink-0\" data-kid=\"83\">\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1656264142377-22ae3fefdbc3?auto=format&w=800&q=80&fit=crop\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80\" alt=\"Mockup 2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-kid=\"84\">\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"w-[500px] h-[300px] bg-[#0e0e0e] rounded-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden shrink-0\" data-kid=\"85\">\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1759563871373-2a7f13ae4b30?auto=format&w=800&q=80&fit=crop\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80\" alt=\"Mockup 3\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-kid=\"86\">\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"w-[500px] h-[300px] bg-[#0e0e0e] rounded-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden shrink-0\" data-kid=\"87\">\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1634744536075-d22f42f88e54?auto=format&w=800&q=80&fit=crop\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80\" alt=\"Mockup 1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-kid=\"88\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"w-[500px] h-[300px] bg-[#0e0e0e] rounded-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden shrink-0\" data-kid=\"89\">\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1656264142377-22ae3fefdbc3?auto=format&w=800&q=80&fit=crop\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80\" alt=\"Mockup 2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-kid=\"90\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"w-[500px] h-[300px] bg-[#0e0e0e] rounded-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden shrink-0\" data-kid=\"91\">\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1759563871373-2a7f13ae4b30?auto=format&w=800&q=80&fit=crop\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80\" alt=\"Mockup 3\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-kid=\"92\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section id=\"contacto\" class=\"py-40 px-6 bg-[#000]\" data-kid=\"93\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center p-12 rounded-[32px] border border-white/10 bg-[#0A0A0A] relative overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"94\">\n      <div class=\"absolute inset-0 glass-glow pointer-events-none\" data-kid=\"95\"></div>\n      \n      <h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-medium tracking-tight mb-6\" data-kid=\"96\">Déjanos tu idea y nos encargamos del resto.</h2>\n      <p class=\"text-white/60 mb-12\" data-kid=\"97\">Cuéntanos sobre tu negocio. Te responderemos con una propuesta clara en menos de 24 horas.</p>\n      \n      <form class=\"space-y-6 text-left relative z-10\" data-kid=\"98\">\n        <div class=\"border-b border-white/20 pb-2\" data-kid=\"99\">\n          <label class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40 mb-1 block\" data-kid=\"100\">Tu nombre</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Alex Pérez\" class=\"bg-transparent w-full outline-none py-2 font-display text-xl placeholder:text-white/10\" data-kid=\"101\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"border-b border-white/20 pb-2\" data-kid=\"102\">\n          <label class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40 mb-1 block\" data-kid=\"103\">Correo electrónico</label>\n          <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"alex@empresa.com\" class=\"bg-transparent w-full outline-none py-2 font-display text-xl placeholder:text-white/10\" data-kid=\"104\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"border-b border-white/20 pb-2\" data-kid=\"105\">\n          <label class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40 mb-1 block\" data-kid=\"106\">¿Cómo podemos ayudarte?</label>\n          <textarea rows=\"2\" placeholder=\"Busco renovar mi página corporativa...\" class=\"bg-transparent w-full outline-none py-2 font-display text-xl placeholder:text-white/10 resize-none\" data-kid=\"107\"></textarea>\n        </div>\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full py-5 bg-white text-black rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/90 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"108\">\n          Enviar solicitud\n          <i class=\"ti ti-send\" data-kid=\"109\"></i>\n        </button>\n      </form>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <footer class=\"py-12 px-6 border-t border-white/5 text-center text-white/20 text-xs\" data-kid=\"110\">\n    <p data-kid=\"111\">© 2026 EDUCA PERÚ — Desarrollo Web de Clase Mundial</p>\n  </footer>\n</div>",
